EN: She styled her long hair in a bun, looking more elegant.

ZH: 他们挽着手臂在公园里散步。
EN: They walked arm in arm in the park.

ZH: 我们挽着臂膀走进了电影院。
EN: We walked into the cinema arm in arm.

